  {
    "index": 3,
    "hash": "uwe67Q5YzVdKdfKoXVanP9m2O4k=",
    "timestampUtcMs": "2026-05-13T13:00:34.000Z",
    "action": {
      "type": "SET_CONTENT",
      "input": {
        "content": "# editors use the modern React hooks pattern from reactor-browser\n\nDocument editors follow a consistent pattern using auto-generated hooks from `@powerhousedao/reactor-browser`:\n\n```typescript\nimport { generateId } from \"document-model/core\";\nimport { useSelectedTodoDocument } from \"../hooks/useTodoDocument.js\";\nimport { addTodo } from \"../../document-models/todo/gen/creators.js\";\n\nexport default function Editor() {\n  const [document, dispatch] = useSelectedTodoDocument();\n\n  function handleAddTodo(values: { title: string }) {\n    if (values.title) {\n      dispatch(addTodo({ id: generateId(), title: values.title }));\n    }\n  }\n}\n```\n\nKey points:\n- `useSelectedXDocument` is auto-generated per document model \u2014 since [[useSelectedDocument hook is auto-generated per document model]], never implement it manually\n- Since [[editors import action creators from gen/creators not from model source]], the import path is `../../document-models/<model>/gen/creators.js`\n- Since [[generateId from document-model/core provides deterministic IDs for dispatch]], IDs are created before dispatch, not inside reducers\n\n---\n\nTopics:\n- [[editor patterns]]\n- [[model-editor wiring]]",
        "updatedAt": "2026-05-13T13:00:34.000Z"
      },
      "timestampUtcMs": "2026-05-13T13:00:34.000Z"
    }
  },
